      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 330i finished in Mineral Grey Metallic with a Black SensaTec interior. This vehicle has served as a reliable daily driver and is in solid condition throughout. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection will reveal standard minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small curb scuff on the rear passenger alloy wheel. The interior is smoke-free and exceptionally clean; the upholstery shows minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all electronic features\u2014including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has a documented service history with synthetic oil changes performed every 7,500 miles, and the brake pads and rotors were replaced within the last year. The turbocharged engine pulls strongly, and the 8-speed transmission shifts seamlessly. This is a well-presented, honest example of a modern sport sedan that offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The sale includes all original owner\u2019s manuals, a clean title, and two sets of keys.",
